text: "Wham Rap! (Enjoy What You Do)" is a 1982 debut single by English pop duo Wham! and is the lead single from their debut studio album Fantastic (1983). It went to number 8 in the United Kingdom, number 9 in Australia and the Netherlands, number 12 in Belgium and did not chart in the United States.
